short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Organize, search, and visualize your tabs!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TabMan is the ultimate tab management tool for power users. If you have too many tabs open and struggle to keep track of them, TabMan is here to help! This Chrome extension automatically organizes your tabs into categories, making it easier to manage them. With a built-in search feature, you can quickly find any tab you need without scrolling through endless tab lists. Visualize your open tabs in a clean, intuitive layout that improves your browsing experience.
